FBIS4-9364 "dreeu080_r_94006" FBIS-EEU-94-080 Daily Report 25 Apr 1994 ROMANIA Army Refutes Allegations Army Refutes Allegations AU2604095494 Bucharest Radio Romania Network in Romanian 1900 GMT 25 Apr 94 AU2604095494 Bucharest Radio Romania Network Romanian BFN [Text] The Press Bureau of the Romanian Army has faxed us a communique in which the Army comments on certain information that appeared in the press regarding allegations that trains with military signs carrying Russian tanks and troops have transited Romania. The Press Office of the Armed Forces mentions that the information issued by the A.M. Press, quoting National Railway Company information, does not correspond to reality. Romania was not asked and consequently did not agree to the transit of military trains belonging to the Russian Federation across its territory, the Press Bureau of the Army states.
